      "title": "City of Mississauga rolls out Parking Enforcement Bike Unit",
      "summary": "This summer, residents and visitors may notice Parking Enforcement Officers on bicycles throughout Mississauga. These officers will patrol parks, waterfront areas, the downtown core, neighbourhood business districts and major community events. Parking Enforcement Officers will engage with residents and visitors, helping educate them about parking rules and responding to concerns in locations that can be difficult to reach by car.",
